comments.content: [Square Sans Pro](http://web.archive.org/web/20090503083144/http:/www.identifont.com/show?PBB) by Panos Vassilou from Parachute.

Renko, did you know that one?  
Or how did you find it?

I was going the [Identifont-way](http://web.archive.org/web/20090503083144/http:/www.identifont.com/identify.html): »Identify a font by appearance«. Here my [result](http://web.archive.org/web/20090503083144/http:/www.identifont.com/identify?12+AYOLIMERECHTSWISSENNEJEWALSENZOSONY+3S9+G39+Z+J+B6G+30E+4A+9Z+11+1A+42+U+M).
Be patient. PF Square Sans Pro comes in the last third of the list.
Hm. I went the same way starting with Hermes and didn’t get there.

If you like: Compare my identifont-decisions to yours: [Link](http://web.archive.org/web/20090503083144/http:/www.identifont.com/identify?11+AYOLIMERECHTSWISSENNEJEWALSENZOSONY+G39+Z+J+B6G+30E+4A+9Z+11+1A+42+U+M).
